---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Work — Cody Smith" description="Selected work across web management, marketing strategy, journalism, and photography.">
  <section class="pt-32 pb-16 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <p class="text-amber-500 font-mono text-sm tracking-wider mb-6">Work</p>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-stone-100 leading-tight mb-8">
        The work that<br />got me here.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-stone-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        A career that looks scattered on paper but follows one thread: find the problem nobody's solving, figure it out, make it work.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Web & Marketing -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 border-t border-stone-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-100 mb-10">Web & Marketing</h2>
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-stone-800 pl-6">
          <p class="text-amber-500 font-mono text-xs tracking-wider mb-1">Current</p>
          <h3 class="text-stone-100 text-lg font-medium">SC Broadband</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-3">Marketing Representative — Cedar City, UT</p>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Sole marketing strategist for a fiber cooperative serving 30,500+ members across Southern Utah and Northern Arizona. Built the dual-brand strategy (residential + managed IT), rebuilt the web presence, launched SEO and content programs from zero. The title says "representative." The work says something different.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-stone-800 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-stone-100 text-lg font-medium">Truvy</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-3">Senior Director of Marketing — Draper, UT</p>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Managed a $2.5M budget and a team of 15+. Moved NPS from 35 to 60. Increased brand recognition 33%. Six months — long enough to prove the model, short enough to know it wasn't the right fit.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-stone-800 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-stone-100 text-lg font-medium">MCC Apparel / H.M. Cole</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-3">Creative Director</p>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Drove +120% in sales. Started in creative, ended up running analytics, data strategy, and marketing operations. Managed a $90K budget. Another role where the job description stopped being accurate about three months in.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-stone-800 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-stone-100 text-lg font-medium">AllenComm</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-3">Technical Writer / Lead Copywriter</p>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Designed the SPTS online training program completed by 50,000+ teachers nationwide. Won Best Advocacy Training Program (Horizon International) and the Davey Award for Education.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Writing & Photography -->
  <section class="py-16 px-6 border-t border-stone-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-100 mb-10">Writing & Photography</h2>
      <div class="space-y-12">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-amber-600/40 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-stone-100 text-lg font-medium">Iron County Today</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-3">Staff Writer & Photographer — Cedar City, UT</p>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Built their digital presence from nothing. Grew the online following 200%. Won Utah Press Association Awards. The first job where I realized what I was actually good at.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-amber-600/40 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-stone-100 text-lg font-medium">Standing Rock</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-3">Photojournalism — 2016–2017</p>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Covered the Dakota Access Pipeline protests. Some of the most important work I've done — not for the portfolio, but for the reminder that showing up matters more than having a plan.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-l-2 border-amber-600/40 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-stone-100 text-lg font-medium">Mt. Rainier Expedition</h3>
          <p class="text-stone-500 text-sm mb-3">Expedition Photographer — SummitClimb</p>
          <p class="text-stone-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Published expedition photography with full credit. A 14,411-foot reminder that the best stories happen when you're too tired to make them up.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 px-6 border-t border-stone-800/50">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <p class="text-stone-400 mb-8">Want to know more about a specific project or see writing samples? Let's talk.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-amber-600 text-stone-950 font-medium text-sm rounded hover:bg-amber-500 transition-colors">
        Get in touch
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
